      &lt;img alt="An illustration of a woman typing on a keyboard, her face replaced with lines of code." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3qdPMCaGAIWhtAiD94vHeqzJBcU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73682410/STK149_AI_Chatbot_K_Radtke.0.jpg" /&gt;
